INSERT INTO products (name, slug, shortDescription, description, regularPrice, categoryId, sku, stock, status, featured, blessingTemple, blessingMaster, blessingDescription, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  '面相分析服务',
  'face-reading-service',
  '传承千年相术，观面知命，解析事业财运、健康婚姻之运势起伏',
  '## 面相分析服务\n\n传承千年相术，观面知命，解析事业财运、健康婚姻之运势起伏。\n\n### 服务内容\n- **十二宫位分析**: 全面解读面部十二宫位的吉凶\n- **流年运势**: 分析未来一年的运势走向\n- **事业财运**: 深度解析事业发展和财富机遇\n- **健康婚姻**: 洞察健康状况和婚姻感情',
  9.90,
  id,
  'FORTUNE-FACE-001',
  9999,
  'published',
  1,
  '五台山',
  '五台山大师',
  '结合传统面相学与现代分析技术',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'fortune-services'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE regularPrice=VALUES(regularPrice), shortDescription=VALUES(shortDescription);

INSERT INTO products (name, slug, shortDescription, description, regularPrice, categoryId, sku, stock, status, featured, blessingTemple, blessingMaster, blessingDescription, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  '手相分析服务',
  'palm-reading-service',
  '掌中乾坤，纹理藏玄机，洞悉人生轨迹，指引命运方向',
  '## 手相分析服务\n\n掌中乾坤，纹理藏玄机，洞悉人生轨迹，指引命运方向。\n\n### 服务内容\n- **三大主线**: 生命线、智慧线、感情线深度解读\n- **财运线**: 分析财富积累和投资运势\n- **事业线**: 洞察职业发展和事业成就\n- **婚姻线**: 解读感情婚姻和人际关系',
  9.90,
  id,
  'FORTUNE-PALM-001',
  9999,
  'published',
  1,
  '五台山',
  '五台山大师',
  '结合传统手相学与现代分析技术',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'fortune-services'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE regularPrice=VALUES(regularPrice), shortDescription=VALUES(shortDescription);

INSERT INTO products (name, slug, shortDescription, description, regularPrice, categoryId, sku, stock, status, featured, blessingTemple, blessingMaster, blessingDescription, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 
  '家居风水服务',
  'fengshui-service',
  '五台山大师堪舆之道，调和气场能量，化解煞气，招财旺运',
  '## 家居风水服务\n\n五台山大师堪舆之道，调和气场能量，化解煞气，招财旺运。\n\n### 服务内容\n- **布局分析**: 全面分析房间布局的风水吉凶\n- **色彩搭配**: 根据五行理论推荐最佳色彩方案\n- **化解煞气**: 识别并提供化解方案\n- **招财旺运**: 提供招财旺运的风水布局建议',
  11.90,
  id,
  'FORTUNE-FENGSHUI-001',
  9999,
  'published',
  1,
  '五台山',
  '五台山大师',
  '结合传统风水学与现代居家设计',
  NOW(),
  NOW()
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'fortune-services'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE regularPrice=VALUES(regularPrice), shortDescription=VALUES(shortDescription);
